Transform odkc_data$track_tally into WAStD LineTransectEncounters.

Source: R/odkc_tt_as_wastd_lte.R
odkc_tt_as_wastd_lte.Rd

Transform odkc_data$track_tally into WAStD LineTransectEncounters.

odkc_tt_as_wastd_lte(data, user_mapping)

Arguments

data

A tibble of parsed ODKC Track Tallies, e.g. odkc_data$track_tally.
user_mapping

.

Value

A tibble suitable to wastd_POST("line-transect-encounters")

Examples

if (FALSE) {
data("odkc_data", package = "wastdr")
user_mapping <- NULL # see odkc_plan for actual user mapping

odkc_data$track_tally %>%
  odkc_tt_as_wastd_lte(user_mapping) %>%
  head(1) %>%
  jsonlite::toJSON()
}
